<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=Visportal&amp;diff#How_visportals_work"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">How visportals work</span></a></li>
<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=Visportal&amp;diff#Placing_a_visportal"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Placing a visportal</span></a></li>
<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=Visportal&amp;diff#Limitations"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Limitations</span></a></li>
<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=Visportal&amp;diff#Distance_based_visportals"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Distance based visportals</span></a></li>
